    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single-condition F1717 protocol; this gap is accepted given the standardized regulatory test method and the corroborating evidence from two independent laboratories. All three primary QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU.",
